'''''Finding Samuel Lowe: From Harlem to China''''', ni film documentaire ya [[Jamayike]] 2015 iyobowe kandi ikorwa na Jeanette Kong<ref>https://www.kinolorber.com/product/finding-samuel-lowe-from-harlem-to-china-dvd</ref>.  Filime irazenguruka uwahoze ari umuyobozi wa tereviziyo, Paula Williams Madison na bakuru be bombi; Elrick na Howard Williams bagiye gushakisha kugira ngo bamenye uko byagendekeye sekuru wabo w'abashinwa witwa Samuel Lowe, wasize nyina wabo w'umushinwa-Jamayike Nell Vera Lowe, mu myaka ya za 1930 muri [[Jamayika|Jamayike]]<ref>https://ttfilmfestival.com/film/finding-samuel-lowe-from-harlem-to-china</ref><ref>https://www.kinolorber.com/film/finding-samuel-lowe-from-harlem-to-china</ref>.  

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://www.libraryjournal.com/?reviewDetail=finding-samuel-lowe-from-harlem-to-china</ref>.  Igitaramo cyacyo cya mbere ku rwego rw’igihugu cyabaye ku ya 14 Gicurasi 2017, Umuyoboro w’isi wa Doc World kandi washyizwe kumurongo ku buntu guhera ku ya 15 Gicurasi - 13 Kamena 2017<ref>https://worldchannel.org/episode/finding-samuel-lowe/</ref>.  Iyi filime yerekanwe ku ya 8 Gashyantare 2014 mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya [[Afurika]] .<ref>http://findingsamuellowe.com/video</ref> 

